Cell["\<\
Resolution: align widths so that cc2 outputs the same number of qubits cc1 \
inputs. Widen the narrow channel (or pad with an identity tensor factor):\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->990070001,ExpressionUUID->"a1b1c1d1-000d-000d-000d-00000000000d"],

